    public class SearchIndexImpl
extends SearchIndexBaseImpl
    The extended model implementation for the SearchIndex service. Represents a row in the "rdconnect.searchindex_rdconnect" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    Helper methods and all application logic should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the SearchIndex interface.

    Robert Reihs
